description: No.1-ranked Sinner, of Italy, prevented Taylor Fritz from ending the American major tennis title drought, less than three weeks after word emerged of Sinner's two positive drug tests.
title: Jannik Sinner beats Taylor Fritz to win U.S. Open, weeks after doping exoneration

description: Mr. Greedy, a beloved member of the Maryland Zoo, was a prolific breeder who helped boost the endangered African penguin population. He died following an age-related health decline, the zoo said.
title: 'Mr. Greedy,' a prolific penguin dad, has died at age 33

description: Over the course of seven decades, Morgenstern helmed major jazz magazines, wrote books, produced concerts, won multiple Grammys, taught college and oversaw one of the world's largest jazz archives.
title: Jazz historian and critic Dan Morgenstern dies at 94

description: The Grammy-winning rapper, who spent this summer topping the charts, previously performed at the 2022 Super Bowl halftime show. But this will be his first Super Bowl as the headliner.
title: Kendrick Lamar will headline next year's Super Bowl halftime show

description: After months of disruption in a massive national feeding effort by global groups, there's a scramble to digitally register more than 6 million Ethiopians to make sure food aid goes to those in need.
title: Why a card with a QR code brings hope to the hungry in Ethiopia

description: The union's members still need to vote on Boeing's proposal and decide whether to authorize a strike if the offer is rejected. If that's the case, a walkout could begin as soon as Friday.
title: Boeing reaches tentative deal with its production workers in hopes to avoid strike

description: The Israeli military said a gunman approached the Allenby Bridge Crossing from the Jordanian side in a truck and opened fire at Israeli security forces, who killed the assailant in a shootout.
title: 3 Israelis killed in attack at West Bank-Jordan border crossing, Israeli military says

description: From school choice to college affordability, Trump and Harris don't have a lot in common. Ahead of the candidates’ only scheduled debate, we’ve put together a handy primer of their education views.
title: Here’s where Trump and Harris stand on 6 education issues

description: The departure of Edmundo González, who Venezuela’s opposition and several foreign governments consider the legitimate winner of July’s presidential race, was announced by Venezuela's vice president.
title: Venezuelan opposition candidate González has left the country for asylum in Spain

description: The fatal collapse of Chance Gainer, a senior at Port St. Joe High School, is the latest in a string of recent deaths of young football players. Seven school athletes died last month.
title: A Florida high school football player died after collapsing during a game
